  "@id": "https://bio.tools/bgpt",
  "@type": "sc:SoftwareApplication",
  "dcterms:conformsTo": "https://bioschemas.org/profiles/ComputationalTool/0.6-DRAFT",
  "sc:description": "BGPT is a REST, Python, and MCP API for searching life-science and biomedical literature and returning structured evidence fields for research agents, literature review workflows, scientific RAG, and evidence dashboards. Results include study context, methods, sample sizes, findings, limitations, conflicts of interest, data and code availability, quality scores, blind spots, and notes on how claims could be falsified.",
